ited Nations]]\n[[Category:Middle Eastern countries]]\n[[Category:Near Eastern countries]]\n[[Category:Southern European countries]]\n[[Category:Western Asian countries]]\n[[Category:States and territories established in 1960]]\n[[Category:Countries in Asia]]\n[[Category:Countries in Europe]]\n[[Category:Greek-speaking countries and territories]]\n[[Category:Turkish-speaking countries and territories]]\n", "name_user": "Interstellarity", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(Added globe to infobox)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyprus"}
